VIM Profile settings
====================

Some VIM options:

:set number  = displays line numbers
:syntax on   = turns on syntax highlighting
:set tabstop=x   = default number of spaces in a tab
:set autoindent=x = set the number of spaces indented automatically

Save these settings the Profile file: .vimrc

inside your home directory:
/home/name
~


To see which vimrc file is being used type: echo $MYVIMRC 
